data.title: Luigi Barzini Jr.
data.meta_description: Luigi Barzini Jr.. Writer: La via del sud. Luigi Barzini Jr. was born on 21 December 1908 in Milan, Lombardy, Italy. He was a writer, known for La via del sud (1953), Oro, donne e maracas (1954) and In einem anderen Land (1957). He was married to Paola Gadola and Giannalisa Gianzana. He died on 30 March 1984 in Rome, Lazio, Italy.
data.text: Luigi Barzini Jr. was born on December 21, 1908 in Milan, Lombardy, Italy. He was a writer, known for La via del sud (1953), Oro, donne e maracas (1954) and In einem anderen Land (1957). He was married to Paola Gadola and Giannalisa Gianzana. He died on March 30, 1984 in Rome, Lazio, Italy.
